*this is a work in progess!*

bss - boring static site generator

+ Getting Started
	bss reads the manifest.ini for configuration options:
	
	```

	[build]
	src=src/
	dest=_site/
	templates_dir=templates
	show_drafts=false
	watch=false

	safe=false
	include=[""]
	exclude=["_site", "*.md"]
	encoding="utf-8"
	markdown_ext="markdown,mkdown,mkdn,mkd,md"

	show_drafts=false

	[server]
	port=1988
	host=127.0.0.1

	```
